{{Quote|The Haunted Straits are said to be guarded by the ghosts of all those Mere lost at sea.|[[Loreli Ro]]|<ref name="Starfighter: Crossbones 3">[[Starfighter: Crossbones 3|''Starfighter: Crossbones'' 3]]</ref>}}
The '''Haunted Straits''' were an area of water of [[Maramere]] that led to [[Invisible Island]]. It was claimed that the straits were inhabited by ghosts, a legend used by [[Sol Sixxa]] when he made them his base of operations for the [[Mere Resistance]].

